name: polyethylene production, high density, granulate, recycled | polyethylene, high density, granulate, recycled | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/16162/documentation

This dataset was built as a weighted average of regional datasets of the same activityName.  Weights are based on production volumes.;Europe without Switzerland: production volume = 2e+09 kg/year, weight = 0.7675;US: production volume = 8e+08 kg/year, weight = 0.2302;CH: production volume = 8e+06 kg/year, weight = 0.00231

Service is starting with the receipt of bales of sorted waste PE

This module includes all processes of the production of recycled PE granulate, high density, up to the factory gate. Machinery infrastructure is excluded

no allocation involved
category: E:Water supply; sewerage, waste management and remediation activities/38:Waste collection, treatment and disposal activities; materials recovery/383:Materials recovery/3830:Materials recovery

processDocumentation.geographyDescription: This dataset is a weighted average built from the following geographies: Europe without Switzerland, US, CH.
processDocumentation.samplingDescription: Uncertainty estimation according to the pedigree matrix
